FBIS3-839 "drafr050_e_94008" FBIS-AFR-94-050 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Mar 1994 WEST AFRICA Mali Public Administration Unions Begin 48-Hour Strike AB1503121394 Bamako Radiodiffusion-Television du Mali Radio in French 0700 GMT 15 Mar 94 AB1503121394 Bamako Radiodiffusion-Television du Mali Radio in French 0700 GMT 15 Mar 94 Language: French Article Type:BFN [Text] The 48-hour strike called by the union committees of public administration establishments starts today and is, in principle, expected to end tomorrow. Consequently, a minimum work schedule will be observed in the affected services.
